{"id":698664855,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"10 months, 3 weeks","timestamp":1652442491,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"29 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/698664855/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Roman to Integer","memory":"8.4 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int romanToInt(string s) {\n        map<char,int>m;\n        m.insert({'I',1});\n        m.insert({'V',5});\n        m.insert({'X',10});\n        m.insert({'L',50});\n        m.insert({'C',100});\n        m.insert({'D',500});\n        m.insert({'M',1000});\n        int sum=0;\n        int i=0;\n        while (i<s.size())\n        {\n            if (m[s[i]]<m[s[i+1]])\n            {\n                sum=sum+m[s[i+1]]-m[s[i]];\n                i=i+2;\n            }\n            else if(m[s[i]]>=m[s[i+1]]){\n                sum=sum+m[s[i]];\n                i=i+1;\n            }\n            \n        }\n        return sum;\n    }\n    \n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"roman-to-integer","has_notes":false}
